# Supplementary-derived tables (public-safety / publication hygiene).
# These CSVs are extracted from Dr. Buckholtz's author-provided Supplementary
# Material and must NOT be redistributed without permission. Local copies are
# preserved; see data/supplementary_extracted/README.md.
data/supplementary_extracted/*.csv

# Author source material — Dr. Buckholtz's preprint (PDF + markdown conversion).
# Kept locally for reference use only. The preprint is CC BY 4.0 (redistribution
# with attribution is permitted), but we do not republish on the author's behalf
# during active collaboration. Track only the README manifest, not the content.
# See data/source_material/README.md.
data/source_material/*
!data/source_material/README.md

# Data files (if large)
# Uncomment if you have large datasets:
# data/*.csv
# data/*.json

# Sensitive correspondence
# DO NOT commit:
# - Email drafts with author
# - Private notes
# - Unpublished materials from Buckholtz

# LaTeX build artifacts
paper/*.aux
paper/*.bbl
paper/*.blg
paper/*.out
paper/*.fls
paper/*.fdb_latexmk
paper/mainNotes.bib

# Experiment output directories
outputs/

# Session-dated scratch experiment scripts (canonical experiments/ is tracked)
experiments/*_2026-*.py

# Author preprint markdown + search result caches (large, re-downloadable)
literature/buckholtz_preprint_v6.md
literature/mech_q*.json
literature/related_work_IDM.md

